From 4e1eb5b6979c65275c17f25a9d8aa75d86d668ab Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Riajul Islam <kmriajulislami@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 12 Mar 2026 16:12:41 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: add markdown preview toggle in diff view for .md files

Add a preview toggle button (eye icon) to the diff card header for
markdown files. When toggled, renders the file content as formatted
markdown instead of showing the raw diff. Supports GitHub Flavored
Markdown (tables, task lists, strikethrough) and Mermaid diagrams
via lazy-loaded rendering.

New components:
- MarkdownPreview: renders markdown with react-markdown + remark-gfm
  + rehype-highlight, with Tailwind-styled elements
- MermaidDiagram: lazy-loads mermaid library for diagram rendering
  with serialized init/render queue to prevent races

Dependencies added: react-markdown, remark-gfm, rehype-highlight, mermaid
